       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. MAXIMUM-CALL.

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.

       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.

       FILE-CONTROL.

       SELECT OUTPUT-FILE ASSIGN TO "MAXIMUM.TXT"
           ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL
           STATUS IS OUTPUT-FILE-STATUS.
       
       DATA DIVISION.

       FILE SECTION.
       FD OUTPUT-FILE.
       01 OUTPUT-RECORD PIC S9(10) SIGN LEADING.

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.

       01 OUTPUT-FILE-STATUS PIC X(02).



       01 LINKED-ITEMS.
           05 L-ARR OCCURS 3 TIMES INDEXED BY NI PIC S9(10).
           05 L-K PIC S9(10).
           05 RESULT OCCURS 100 TIMES INDEXED BY NJ PIC S9(10).

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.

       MOVE 1 TO L-ARR(1)
       MOVE 2 TO L-ARR(2)
       MOVE 3 TO L-ARR(3)
       MOVE 1 TO L-K

       CALL "MAXIMUM" USING LINKED-ITEMS
       
       OPEN OUTPUT OUTPUT-FILE

       IF OUTPUT-FILE-STATUS NOT = "00"
           DISPLAY "ERROR OPENING OUTPUT FILE"
           STOP RUN
        END-IF

       PERFORM VARYING NJ FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL NJ > 100
           MOVE RESULT (NJ) TO OUTPUT-RECORD
           WRITE OUTPUT-RECORD
       END-PERFORM

        IF OUTPUT-FILE-STATUS NOT = "00"
            DISPLAY "ERROR WRITING TO OUTPUT FILE"
            STOP RUN
        END-IF

        CLOSE OUTPUT-FILE
        .
       